{% extends "base.html.twig" %}

{% block body %}


<div class="card-group support mt-3 mt-lg-5">
    <div class="card ">
        <h1 class="h1 card-title p-3">Welcome to Royal Road Watch!</h1>
        <div class="card-body">

    <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <p>Hi there! I’m <strong>Siderate Incon</strong>, the creator of Royal Road Watch. This site is dedicated to providing authors and readers with valuable insights, updates, and analytics related to Royal Road. Whether you're an aspiring writer looking to track your progress or a reader wanting to stay informed, you're in the right place!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-4">
        <h3>Why I Started This Site</h3>
        <p>Although I’m relatively new to web novels and online fiction, I have many author friends who have built their journeys on Royal Road. I noticed a gap in the available tools for tracking stats and progress, so I created Royal Road Watch to fill that need. My goal is to make it easier for authors to access the insights they need—all in one convenient place.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mb-4">
        <h3>Why Trust Me?</h3>
        <p>I’ve spent countless hours navigating Royal Road, exploring its community, and understanding the trends that shape its stories. My goal is to provide accurate, timely, and well-researched updates so you can always be in the know. I take pride in being both engaging and trustworthy.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mb-4">
        <h3>The "About Me" section wouldn't be complete without some random things I like:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Urban fantasy TV and novels</li>
            <li>Discussing books and writing with fellow enthusiasts</li>
            <li>Exploring new storytelling platforms and trends</li>
            <li>Devouring unacceptable quantities of coffee while writing my own novels</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center">
        <h3>Let’s Connect!</h3>
        <p>I’d love to hear from you! Whether you have feedback, a question, or just want to chat about books, feel free to reach out.</p>
    </div>


        </div>
    </div>
</div>





<div class="card-group mt-3 mt-lg-5">
    <div class="card border-dark p-5">
        <h4 class="card-title p-2 mb-3 text-center">Free Features</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Track any story you like, as many stories as you like.</li>
            <li>Get an alert when any story you're tracking hits <strong>20th</strong> place or higher.</li>
            <li>Track all of the <strong>standard</strong> genre Rising Stars lists (action, comedy, romance, etc), as well as the Main list itself.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
        
    <div class="card border-dark p-5">
        <h4 class="card-title p-2 mb-3 text-center">Patron Features</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>All of the free</strong>, plus...</li>
            <li>Get an alert when any story you're tracking hits <strong>50th</strong> place or higher.</li>
            <li>Track all of the <strong>hidden</strong> genres Rising Stars lists (dungeon, time-travel, xianxia, gender-bender, etc).</li>
            <li>View advanced analytics, such as highest rank over time.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="card-group">
            <div class="card border-light justify-content-center">
                <img src="{{ asset('assets/images/ranking.png') }}" class="card-img-top mx-center" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#rankingModal" style="cursor: pointer;" alt="Ranking photo thumbnail">
                <div class="modal fade" id="rankingModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
                    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered modal-xl">
                        <div class="modal-content">
                            <div class="modal-body text-center">
                                <img src="{{ asset('assets/images/ranking.png') }}" class="img-fluid" alt="Ranking photo">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
                
            <div class="card border-light justify-content-center">
                <img src="{{ asset('assets/images/ratings.png') }}" class="card-img-top mx-center" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#ratingsModal" style="cursor: pointer;" alt="Ratings photo thumbnail">
                <div class="modal fade" id="ratingsModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
                    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered modal-xl">
                        <div class="modal-content">
                            <div class="modal-body text-center">
                                <img src="{{ asset('assets/images/ratings.png') }}" class="img-fluid" alt="Ratings photo">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card-group support mt-3 mt-lg-5">
    <div class="card text-center border-dark">
        <div class="card-img-overlay card-title d-flex flex-column justify-content-between border" style="height:100%">
            <h4 class="card-title p-3 text-center"><strong>Get</strong> Support</h4>
            <div class="alert alert-info mt-3" role="alert" style="opacity: 85%">
                <p class="card-text">Spot something that's not working right, confused and need help, or just want to see the code?</p>
                <p class="card-text">Check out <a href="https://github.com/inconsiderate/rs_tracker">GitHub</a> to report issues, or ask for help.</p>        
            </div>
        </div>
        <img src="{{ asset('assets/images/helpyou.png') }}" class="card-img-top mx-auto" alt="...Help you.">
    </div>
    <div class="card text-center border-dark">
        <div class="card-img-overlay card-title d-flex flex-column justify-content-between border" style="height:100%">
            <h4 class="card-title p-3 text-center"><strong>Give</strong> Support</h4>
            <a href="https://www.patreon.com/inconsiderate/membership"><img src="{{ asset('assets/images/patreon.jpg') }}" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Become a Patron"></a>
            <div class="alert alert-info mt-3" role="alert" style="opacity: 85%">
                <br/><a href="/profile">Become a Patron to Unlock Subscriber Benefits</a><br/><br/><p><p/>
            </div>
        </div>
        <img src="{{ asset('assets/images/helpme.png') }}" class="card-img-top mx-auto" alt="Help me...">
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}